= User preferences =

On this page, the user's preferences can be set.

== Preferred language ==
{{#widget: CodeExecution | 
 clazz = 'com.fluidops.iwb.util.user.UserPreferencesUIUtil'
 | method = 'setLocale'
 | passContext = true
 | render = 'inline'
 | label = 'Set Locale'
 | args = {{ '%locale' }}
 | userInput = {{ 
      {{ name = 'locale'
       | componentType = 'PLAIN'
       | displayName = 'Preferred language'
       | description = 'User's preferred language'
       | dataType = 'xsd:string'
       | presetValue = $Java:com.fluidops.iwb.util.user.UserPreferencesUIUtil#getLocaleAsTupleQueryResult$
       | selectValues = {{ '"en"' | '"de"' }}
      }} }}
 | onFinish = 'reloadComponent'
}}

{{Settings:Breadcrumbs}}



